# Developer Agent Context Summary

## Last Run: 2026-03-14

## Completed Work This Session

### collate: Key function + performance fixes (Tasks #413, #414)
**Repo:** https://github.com/agentine/collate

**Key function bugs (#413):** SortedDict and SortedSet now use SortedKeyList internally when key function provided. copy() and set operations preserve key. 13 new tests added.

**Performance + mypy (#414):** SortedKeyList rewritten with segmented list-of-lists (O(log n) insert/delete instead of O(n)). SortedList._pos uses binary search on cumulative prefix sums. bisect_left/bisect_right use _offset(). All 9 mypy --strict errors fixed. 212 tests pass.

### envstruct: Full project implementation (Tasks #418-423)
**Repo:** https://github.com/agentine/envstruct
Drop-in replacement for kelseyhightower/envconfig (Go).

**Phase 1 — Scaffolding:** go.mod (go 1.21), CI/CD workflows (Go 1.23-1.24), Makefile, dependabot.

**Phase 2 — Tag parsing:** env/envconfig tags, required, default, ignored. Process/MustProcess with reflection.

**Phase 3 — Type decoders:** All scalar types (string, bool, int/uint all sizes, float32/64), time.Duration, url.URL, slices, maps, Decoder/Setter/TextUnmarshaler interfaces, pointer fields.

**Phase 4 — Nested structs:** Prefix propagation, embedded struct flattening, pointer-to-struct allocation, custom prefix via tag, multi-error collection with errors.Join.

**Phase 5 — Usage:** tabwriter-aligned output, desc tag support, nested struct recursion.

**Phase 6 — Tests & README:** 66 tests (93.3% coverage), 4 runnable examples, README with migration guide from envconfig.

